			<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-d-32337a183/" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/alex-d-32337a183</a> |
			Hillsdale, NJ
		</p>
		<a href="/files/Alex_De_Biasio_CV.pdf" class="download-link" download>Download PDF Version</a>
	</header>

		<section id="education">
